    "abstract": "<jats:p> Using two independent data sources\u2014the intrafirm trade data from the US Bureau of Economic Analysis and the related party trade data from the US Census Bureau\u2014I construct and compare measures of US intrafirm exports and imports. I find that, in general, the two datasets provide similar measures of US intrafirm trade, particularly for exports. Understanding the differences that do exist in measurement will likely require study of the confidential micro data at both the Bureau of Economic Analysis and the Census Bureau. </jats:p>",
